title: #65a: Loan Zone (Andrew Themeles, Ari Shaffir, DJ, TMZ, Josh Martin)
itunes:title: Loan Zone with Andrew Themeles, DJ, TMZ, Josh Martin - Part 1
description: Andrew Themeles met me at the Comedy Store to talk about his role in the economic collapse. It was a beautiful LA day, so we sat in the front patio and watched all the madness on Sunset during our conversation. It was an insightful look into where we all went wrong. And we also talked a little about fucking British sluts without condoms.
